summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Twenty-third Avenue northwest from West Seventieth Street to West Seventy-fifth Street in the City of Seattle, by constructing water mains under Ordinance No. 17705 creating Local Improvement District No. 1682 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
